N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 17.2 - Investigation

State Regulations

The director of the Office of Professional Discipline or that
officer's designee shall, in matters involving possible professional
misconduct, initiate an investigation of each such complaint or other
information. Notes
